info.name: Vintage Vanilla Bon Bons
info.description: Vintage Vanilla - Savor the timeless delight of Vintage Vanilla Bonbons with zero sugar. A box holds 9 bite-sized, creamy ice cream treats, each just 30 calories. Enjoy the classic taste of vanilla in a guilt-free, zero-sugar indulgence that's perfect for any occasion!

info.name: Classic Chocobar
info.description: Experience the nostalgia of creamy vanilla wrapped in a rich chocolate coating. 113 calories only and zero added sugar.

info.name: Mango Duet
info.description: Transport yourself to the tropics with velvety vanilla encased in a real mango shell. 60 calories only and zero added sugar.

info.name: Belgian Dark Chocolate 100ml
info.description: Indulge in our Zero Sugar Belgian Dark Chocolate, a rich delight capturing finest cocoa essence. Crafted sans added sugar, perfect for health-conscious and weight watchers. Share guilt-free or savor solo - each 100ml serving, 79 calories, abounds with pure pleasure and benefits.

info.name: Mad Over Mango 100ml
info.description: Experience the essence of Ratnagiri Alphonso Mangoes all year round with our delectable creation. Crafted for true mango aficionados, this treat is a celebration of real and ripe Alphonso Mangoes. With only 67 calories per 100ml, our mango delight is a guilt-free pleasure that boasts a host of benefits.

info.name: Malai Kulfi 100ml
info.description: Savor guilt-free pleasure with our handcrafted Malai Kulfi Ice Creams. Luxuriate in the creamy, velvety texture, a symphony of comfort and indulgence. With a distinctive taste and just 83 calories per 100ml, each bite delivers pure milk bliss.

info.name: Cold Brew Coffee 100ml
info.description: For those who relish the ritual of sipping coffee, prepare to succumb once more. That same aromatic, creamy, and utterly addictive flavor now takes form in delectable scoops that will leave you craving for more. It's time for a cuppa with a twist. With just 93 calories per 100ml, this creation offers a host of advantages.

info.name: Sassy Strawberry 100ml
info.description: Experience the pure allure of luscious, handpicked strawberries from the serene environs of Mahabaleshwar, transformed into a burst of sassiness that's captured in our exquisite strawberry ice cream. Indulge without worry, as each calorie can be easily counted. With zero artificial flavors, colors, or preservatives, this treat is designed to uplift your day. Only 93 calories per serving!

info.name: Madagascar Chocolate Bar
info.description: Delight in our premium Madagascar chocolate bar – a harmonious blend of rich cocoa and health-conscious choices. Enjoy extra crunch and flavor, with natural sugar substitute for guilt-free indulgence. At just 99 calories per serving, it's the ultimate chocolate experience that satisfies both taste and well-being.

info.name: Nutty Butterscotch 100ml
info.description: Elevate your dessert experience with Nutty Butterscotch Ice Cream from our Zero Sugar Range. Luxuriate in velvety ice cream swirled with indulgent butterscotch and adorned with toasted almond and cashew pieces. The fusion of smoothness and crunch, with just 86 calories per 100ml, offers a guilt-free symphony of flavors.

info.name: Mocha Brownie Fudge 100ml
info.description: Discover the harmony of taste and wellness with Mocha Brownie Fudge ice cream. Enjoy tender chocolate brownie layers woven with mocha coffee richness and fortified with whey protein. Twice the protein of regular ice cream, zero added sugar, artificial additives, or preservatives. Delight guilt-free with each 100ml serving at just 79 kcal.

info.name: Hazelnut Chocolate Bar
info.description: Savor our low-calorie Hazelnut Chocolate Bar Ice Cream, a high-protein delight boasting 5g protein in a 70mL bar. Crafted from premium cocoa and hazelnuts, it's a guilt-free indulgence that delights your taste buds and supports your goals.

info.name: Blueberry Cheesecake 100ml
info.description: Savor the perfect balance of velvety cheesecake and tangy blueberries. Our Blueberry Cheesecake ice cream boasts real European blueberries and 2.5x the protein of regular ice cream. No added sugar, artificial color, flavor, or preservatives. With low glycemic index and high fiber, this nutritional powerhouse delivers an explosion of flavors. A 100ml serving is a symphony of delight.

info.name: O. M. G. Chocolate Bar
info.description: Delight in the harmonious layers that form this sinful yet guilt-free delight. A crunchy chocolate coating envelops a creamy vegan ice cream middle layer, all encasing a heart of smooth dark chocolate. This exquisite creation is the pinnacle of taste without the compromise on your well-being.

info.name: Alphonso & Peach 100ml
info.description: Savor the delightful blend of real Alphonso mangoes and sweet peaches in our vegan frozen dessert. It's a dairy-free, cholesterol-free, and gluten-free treat with only 76 calories per 100ml. Pure fruity bliss without any artificial additives.

info.name: O. M. G. Chocolate 100ml
info.description: Experience pure bliss with OMG Chocolate – a velvety symphony of flavor from finest Ghana cocoa. Dairy-free, additive-free, and preservative-free, this vegan delight delights guilt-free. Revel in rich cocoa notes with zero trans-fat, cholesterol, and gluten. Just 98 calories per 100ml, it's a balanced treat for senses and soul.

info.name: Jack Of All Fruits 100ml
info.description: Savor the extraordinary with Jack of All Fruits, a lusciously creamy vegan ice cream that redefines indulgence. Crafted from exotic jackfruit, rich coconut milk, soy, and natural wonders, this treat delivers an unparalleled taste experience. Embrace healthful delight as you relish its zero added sugar, preservatives, gluten, and cholesterol. A symphony of flavors awaits—pure pleasure with no compromises. Each 100ml serving offers a mere 80 Kcal.

info.name: Tropical Mango Pops 70ml
info.description: Savor year-round delight with zero-sugar Alphonso Mango popsicle. Embrace authentic mango bliss, free from additives or preservatives. At 46 calories per serving, relish guilt-free pleasure enriched with Vitamin C and fiber. Elevate your indulgence with the true essence of mango, a nourishing treat for all seasons.

info.name: Lychee Royale Pops 70 Ml
info.description: Elevate your senses with our Lychee Fruit Popsicles—bursting with tropical sweetness and zero added sugar. Each bite reveals succulent lychee essence, accompanied by Vitamin C. At only 51 calories, enjoy guilt-free indulgence with no added sugar or preservatives, a symphony of vibrant flavor and health.

info.name: Jamun Sriracha Pops 70ml
info.description: Relive carefree summers with Jamun Sriracha popsicle, a nostalgic journey to childhood. Immerse in sweet tanginess, fruit magic fortified with Vitamin C. Jamun's tartness and Sriracha's spice create a divine 39-calorie symphony.

info.name: Valencia Orange Pops 70ml
info.description: Immerse in sun-kissed oranges transformed into sublime popsicles. A dance of sweet and tangy on your taste buds, invigorated by Vitamin C. Relish guilt-free with zero added sugar, 59 calories per serving, pure zestful joy.

info.name: Spicy Guava Pops 70ml
info.description: Escape with Guava Ice Candy - a vibrant life essence. Infused with luscious guava, this popsicle radiates tropical warmth. Vitamin C and fiber burst, hint of masala ignites a tantalizing explosion. 45 calories, real guava goodness, and spicy thrill await.

info.name: Tender Coconut Pops 70ml
info.description: Immerse in our Tender Coconut Pop - a guilt-free, tropical symphony crafted from coconut Malai, water, and natural sweeteners. The velvety embrace and luscious flavor create a heavenly sensation. With 78 kcal per serving (70ml), indulge in this guilt-free treasure trove of natural goodness and delight.
